@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Dashboard Staff Today (STAFF+)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/staff-today
X-Staff-Role: STAFF
X-Staff-Id: demo-staff

### Dashboard Staff Summary for Explicit Date (STAFF+)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/staff-today?date=2026-03-10
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: demo-manager
